name: posion girl - modern woman witch
description:
this is my first work to jump in NFT in hicentnunc
a little story from this year's halloween of romantic life, my concern for women i call it " posion girl - modern woman witch " why? I realized that every woman's words can never be rejected, what they want we always obey, even though it will have to make us these women are not gloomy angry or sad,
This is my conclusion on Halloween this year, women are one of the real forms of horror, we are aware and we are swallowed by it. by helloottit for all those who are struggling in their love story :)
